{"tid":2191273,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企啲主子話想同我過中秋，於是....","createTime":"2020-09-06T10:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T03:14:36.000Z","uid":306018,"like":90,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"720eab748292ecaa3daa99742b7576c9fd3db3c6","tid":2191273,"uid":306018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:43:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>小弟作為動物傳心師，平時除左同啲龜仔傾下計之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMrHDk3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMrHDk3.jpg&h=11d5361b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1WXsep.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1WXsep.jpg&h=52a9ce82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>得閒亦都會向屋企既老細詢問下佢地有冇不滿既地方，我可以點改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFJOyWa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFJOyWa.jpg&h=27a0c02c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FeVk9uv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFeVk9uv.jpg&h=1b47383d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5LUVdWf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5LUVdWf.png&h=cc09a5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPrkp20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPrkp20.png&h=9e0ee922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>直到早排我屋企既老細開聲同我講...<br />\n <span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"large\">:</span></span>就到中秋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地又有得食燈籠玩月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人諗過屋企啲貓狗既感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">佢地都想食月餅啊</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53gAdYo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53gAdYo.jpg&h=8442bd78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RNrgHRK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRNrgHRK.jpg&h=c0104a3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OcxLBbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOcxLBbL.jpg&h=99569470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">於是！</span></span>由<span class=\"gold\">本地黃店</span>以手足班底全人手製作既<span class=\"gold\">黃色寵物月餅</span>🥮就出現啦</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\"><strong>為左俾大家同主子食住月餅共渡中秋，仲可以捐錢俾浪浪同手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請容許我向大家隆重介紹！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\"><p class=\"center\"><strong>【毛．手伴禮，毛孩x手足兩團圓】</strong></p></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CjL5Bgf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjL5Bgf.jpg&h=84575569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"large\">月餅．起源<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<strong>香港既人同動物一直經歷社會上既不公。一年過去，香港人一直<span class=\"red\">「 #加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</span>，⼀直<span class=\"red\">「 #反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span>，團結一致。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">「我地嘅寵物月餅可以冇蘋果，但係香港人唔可以冇蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</span></span></strong></p><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4y9mUwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4y9mUwi.jpg&h=cc3e8631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於2020年中秋，狗寶寶寵物店製作出「毛．手伴禮」寵物月餅，除左希望毛孩同主人可以有個開心中秋節，同時更想幫助有需要既香港人同毛孩。是次活動將會有<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">百分之二十收益予「保護傘計劃」及「毛浪孩」動物義工組織，作支援抗爭與流浪動物用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span></span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"purple\"><strong><span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"large\">早鳥優惠: 於2020年9月14日或之前訂購，可享早鳥價HKD$69/盒</span></strong></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong>原價:  HKD$79/盒</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"limegreen\">口味: 蕃薯雞肉花膠甘筍</span> (一盒兩隻)</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\"><strong>保鮮期: 月餅<span class=\"red\">絕無添加任何防腐劑</span>，冷藏可保存約4-5天，全人手製作。冷藏可保存約4-5天。為確保月餅品質，客人:<br />\n- 購買2盒或以下，可選擇以$10加購冰袋一個<br />\n- 購買3盒或以上，可免費獲得冰袋一個</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">重點來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！訂購方法:</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"large\">- 狗寶寶兩間分店(置樂店及建生店購買月餅卷)<br />\n<br />\n- 本店網站:<a href=\"http://www.doggiebobo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.doggiebobo.com&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4pggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=f0475064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.doggiebobo.com</a><br />\n<br />\n- Whatsapp: 96828451 或Facebook、Instagram DM<br />\n</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"violet\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\"><strong><span class=\"large\">換領方法:<br />\n<br />\n- 狗寶寶門市及<span class=\"gold\">指定各區黃店 </span>(21/9-1/10/2020 營業時間內)，領取時向店員出示月餅卷或電子收據編號及姓名即可<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4szuWa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4szuWa.jpg&h=04d01c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 購買滿$300或加$30運費送貨服務(送貨服務只限:28/9-30/9/2020)</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n* 數量有限，售完即止<br />\n<br />\n* 產品相片只供參考<br />\n<br />\n* 客人須於有效日期內換取月餅，逾期作廢<br />\n<br />\n* 換領地點或有機會作出修改或增加，最新換領地點及資訊請瀏覽本店網站<br />\n<br />\n* 狗寶寶DoggieBoBo 保留修改優惠條款及細則、更改或終止此優惠之權利，恕不另行通知<br />\n<br />\n* 如有任何爭議，狗寶寶Doggie Bo Bo 保留最終決定權"},{"pid":"e2c1e4d043b3291815bc4fd48b3c0deae6cc2200","tid":2191273,"uid":306018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:44:26.000Z","msg":"俾大家睇下我屋企啲貓狗幾可愛！！！推！！"},{"pid":"1296aa8e43d2b313b6a33600c758180eab2d46c7","tid":2191273,"uid":306018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"中秋買月餅俾毛孩啊啊啊，推！！！"},{"pid":"c9126f95bbcc36ce4e96e390cd22279e5d2195d3","tid":2191273,"uid":306018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"得你食冇佢食！！唔得啊！！！推！！"},{"pid":"ad53171806b17fd84caef9f902850cfad4f00735","tid":2191273,"uid":306018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"會捐錢俾手足同流浪動物架！一齊推！！"},{"pid":"905c60b58c9f1dc1bb75c0c0164afd7f354973a8","tid":2191273,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f15d636905d40ac0fd5ec9dcea800035cf66a92","tid":2191273,"uid":306018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"